106
00:05:30,378 --> 00:05:32,138
Or you may pass away anytime.

107
00:05:32,777 --> 00:05:35,296
Mr. Li, let's send you home to rest.

108
00:05:35,296 --> 00:05:36,160
No.

109
00:05:36,657 --> 00:05:37,578
Mrs. Chun.

110
00:05:37,578 --> 00:05:39,578
Please don't drive me away, okay?

111
00:05:40,698 --> 00:05:42,097
