142
00:07:44,618 --> 00:07:46,537
You're obviously better than yesterday.

143
00:07:47,897 --> 00:07:50,417
The key is to stay cheerful.

144
00:07:50,417 --> 00:07:52,217
Don't pressure yourself.

145
00:07:52,818 --> 00:07:54,217
