146
00:07:54,618 --> 00:07:57,097
It's a gain
whenever I survive another day.

147
00:07:58,097 --> 00:08:00,258
Don't be so petty. Just eat.

148
00:08:00,818 --> 00:08:01,696
Alright.

149
00:08:07,938 --> 00:08:08,800
Peilan.

150
00:08:09,618 --> 00:08:10,496
