195
00:10:09,577 --> 00:10:10,496
Peilan.

196
00:10:11,177 --> 00:10:12,096
Peilan.

197
00:10:13,177 --> 00:10:14,112
Mr. Lu.

198
00:10:15,258 --> 00:10:16,537
You're leaving?

199
00:10:19,378 --> 00:10:20,288
Mr. Lu, rest assured.

200
00:10:20,537 --> 00:10:21,577
I'll find a chance

201
00:10:21,577 --> 00:10:22,618
