225
00:11:15,297 --> 00:11:16,138
Mr. Lu.

226
00:11:16,777 --> 00:11:17,657
Mr. Lu.

227
00:11:27,657 --> 00:11:28,576
Peilan.

228
00:11:28,777 --> 00:11:30,858
What a lovely day for a pleasant

229
00:11:34,537 --> 00:11:35,392
