236
00:11:50,577 --> 00:11:52,937
No, I'm trying to say...

237
00:11:55,218 --> 00:11:56,937
Are you okay? Should we go back?

238
00:11:56,937 --> 00:11:57,792
No need.

239
00:11:58,618 --> 00:11:59,458
Maybe I'm carsick.

240
00:12:02,177 --> 00:12:03,104
Peilan.

241
00:12:04,498 --> 00:12:05,577
