243
00:12:13,378 --> 00:12:13,856
Giddyap!

244
00:12:13,856 --> 00:12:14,208
Stop!

245
00:12:14,208 --> 00:12:14,817
Giddyap!

246
00:12:14,817 --> 00:12:16,378
