259
00:12:38,738 --> 00:12:39,648
Alright.

260
00:12:39,648 --> 00:12:40,498
No.

261
00:12:40,498 --> 00:12:41,577
Just get in.

262
00:12:42,098 --> 00:12:42,944
Hurry up.

263
00:12:46,098 --> 00:12:46,976
Peilan.

264
00:12:47,177 --> 00:12:48,537
It's not like I don't trust you.

265
00:12:48,777 --> 00:12:49,978
I know, Mr. Lu.

266
00:12:50,218 --> 00:12:52,057
I'm just worried about Mr. Li.

267
00:12:52,498 --> 00:12:53,344
I understand.

268
00:12:55,218 --> 00:12:56,537
This is the broken one.

269
00:12:57,777 --> 00:12:59,498
You're so careless, Mr. Lu.

270
00:13:00,128 --> 00:13:01,057
