277
00:13:17,697 --> 00:13:18,656
Look at him.

278
00:13:18,937 --> 00:13:19,777
Let him be.

279
00:13:21,138 --> 00:13:21,984
Look.

280
00:13:22,912 --> 00:13:23,808
Isn't it pretty?

281
00:13:23,808 --> 00:13:24,672
Yeah.

282
00:13:53,657 --> 00:13:54,560
"Poopoo"?

283
00:14:14,897 --> 00:14:16,577
Banxia, you're counting money?

284
00:14:17,858 --> 00:14:18,777
